      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered, garage-kept, and is looking for a new owner who will love it as much as I have. If you\u2019re looking for something that feels brand new without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44500.0,
