    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S represents a pinnacle of mechanical preservation. Powered by a 3.6L flat-six with a direct-drive 6-speed manual transaxle, this wide-body variant features an advanced viscous-clutch AWD system for optimized torque distribution. The M96 powerplant has undergone proactive IMS bearing replacement and RMS servicing, ensuring peak operational integrity. The chassis retains its factory-honed suspension geometry, complemented by four-piston monobloc 'Big Red' calipers and cross-drilled rotors for exceptional thermal management. Every tactile surface and mechanical linkage remains in superlative condition, offering a visceral, analog driving experience for the discerning collector.",
      "price": 48500.0,
