    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been preserved with obsessive care. Kept exclusively in a climate-controlled garage, the original factory paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with no swirl marks, chips, or scratches. Inside, the cabin still carries that new-car scent; the premium leather upholstery is free of any creasing or bolster wear, and every electronic component functions with crisp, factory-spec precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, supported by a complete, organized binder of every service record since its purchase. We have recently performed a preventative fluid flush and a multi-point inspection to ensure it remains in peak operating condition. The sale includes the original window sticker, two sets of keys, and the factory-issued floor mats in untouched condition. This is a collector-grade example for a buyer who demands perfection.",
